            {
                "id": 15,
                "name": "Plant Problem Type",
                "description": "Get more information about a problem that occurred. Possible outcomes:\r\n\r\n- **Unusable Amenities** \u2014 employees don't appreciate this kind of work environment\r\n- **Low Wages** \u2014 employees are unhappy and may go on strike\r\n- **Waste Bacteria Inert** \u2014 fail to reduce radioactive waste\r\n- **Radioactive Waste Leak** \u2014 significantly increases amount of radioactive waste (cleanup becomes a bigger job)\r\n- **Cooling System Leak** \u2014 less efficient thermal waste reduction, could potentially hit employees with scalding water\r\n- **Mechanical Failure** \u2014 temporarily prevents some systems from operating, may require mechanical repairs\r\n- **Electricity Down** \u2014 temporarily prevents some systems from operating, may require repairs to electrical system\r\n- **Energy Not Gained** \u2014 nothing to fix but roll back recent energy gains\r\n- **Excess Energy** \u2014 this is a bigger problem, damaging storage systems\r\n- **Core Meltdown** \u2014 the worst-case scenario\r\n\r\nIf the inciting roll was a major failure then consider the problem to be more severe.",
                "attribs": [],
                "abilities": [],
